org.bukkit.inventory.meta

Interface PotionMeta

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cloneable, ConfigurationSerializable, ItemMeta, PersistentDataHolder

    public interface PotionMeta
extends ItemMeta
    Represents a potion or item that can have custom effects.
